<a href="https://preactjs.com" target="_blank">
<p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/preactjs/preact/8b0bcc927995c188eca83cba30fbc83491cc0b2f/logo.svg?sanitize=true" alt="Preact" title="Preact"></p>
</a>
</p>
<p align="center">Fast <b>3kB</b> alternative to React with the same modern API.</p>
<p><strong>All the power of Virtual DOM components, without the overhead:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Familiar React API &amp; patterns: ES6 Class, hooks, and Functional Components</li>
<li>Extensive React compatibility via a simple <a href="https://github.com/preactjs/preact/tree/master/compat" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">preact/compat<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> alias</li>
<li>Everything you need: JSX, <abbr title="Virtual DOM">VDOM</abbr>, <a href="https://github.com/preactjs/preact-devtools" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">DevTools<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>, <abbr title="Hot Module Replacement">HMR</abbr>, <abbr title="Server-Side Rendering">SSR</abbr>.</li>
<li>Highly optimized diff algorithm and seamless hydration from Server Side Rendering</li>
<li>Supports all modern browsers and IE11</li>
<li>Transparent asynchronous rendering with a pluggable scheduler</li>
</ul>
